                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Here’s the simple breakdown:</p><ul><li><strong>HydroTumbler:</strong> up to ~3000 PPB in ~10 minutes (portable, rechargeable)</li><li><strong>HydroPitcher:</strong> up to ~1500 PPB in ~10 minutes (family-size, countertop plug-in)</li><li>Hydrator Pro: Flagship 5.14PPM Hydrogen Water Bottle<br/></li></ul><p>Pick <strong>Tumbler</strong> for daily carry + gym + travel. <br/>Pick <strong>Hydrator Pro</strong> for Performance.<br/>Pick <strong>Pitcher</strong> for a family. <br/><br/>PS - Try <a href=\"https://drwater.store/products/hydrobase-6-stage-countertop-water-purifier\" title=\"https://drwater.store/products/hydrobase-6-stage-countertop-water-purifier\">Dr.Water Hydrogen RO</a> (RO +UV) with Hydrogen and Instant Hot/Cold Water</p>",
